\mathrm{\mathbf{H}}\left(\sigma_{y}^{2}\,-\,2\busigma^{\prime}\,\bubeta\,+\,\bubeta^{\prime}\,\mathrm{\mathbf{C}}\,\bubeta\right) & =2\,\mathrm{\mathbf{C}}.\label{eq:LMMSE3a}
\end{align}

